{"tid":1864823,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"高中以下延後2周開學　泌尿科醫師建議：割包皮絕佳時機！","createTime":"2020-02-05T22:05:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-06T06:49:18.000Z","uid":4260,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"90f231586864230f15535f00ef82359cddb03e0f","tid":1864823,"uid":4260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T22:05:51.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎疫情全球擴散，教育部2日宣布高中以下延至2月25日開學，等於學生們可以多放2周寒假。對此泌尿科醫師李嘉文就在粉專PO文開玩笑表示：「真是學生族群來割包皮的絕佳時機」，因為學生們怕開學時間不方便手術的問題，通通都不存在了。<br />\n<br />\n李嘉文在粉專PO文表示，「這個寒假真的是學生族群割包皮的絶佳時機，之前無法排入手術排程的、怕開學寒輔不方便的問題通通不存在了」。<br />\n<br />\n李嘉文表示，很多家長都認為割包皮後不太能夠洗澡，所以大部分家長都會在冬天帶小朋友來割包皮，不過割完後其實當天就可以洗澡，簡單用塑膠袋套著就可以了，所以其實冬夏並無差別。<br />\n<br />\n李嘉文指出，做完手術恢復期大約是3個禮拜，割完包皮後會給予3天份的抗生素，預防傷口感染機會，之後其實就不需要吃藥。<br />\n<br />\n不過李嘉文也提醒，割完包皮後要注意，早上可能會勃起，所以建議：「一早起床，眼睛一睜開，就趕快跳起來去廁所小便」，或是看到路邊有美女，也趕快去廁所小便轉移注意力，傷口就不會那麼痛了。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://health.ettoday.net/news/1637814\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhealth.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F1637814&d=SLV77eIUGxkMmCzjf2iSt4lFrThteLnMWGuqQSPs63E%3D&h=600a1502\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://health.ettoday.net/news/1637814</a>"},{"pid":"4572748d8d973fbd7b846f72d6b0b5e04b332aca","tid":1864823,"uid":175346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T22:18:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"be22a50e796e0d92fde9446d539cc9bc5afae222","tid":1864823,"uid":213607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T22:24:40.000Z","msg":"割包皮預防肺炎 即刻好生意<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce0806ca6754b011d8e4a5b79e35cb40e8d2e0f4","tid":1864823,"uid":131188,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"be22a50e796e0d92fde9446d539cc9bc5afae222","tid":1864823,"uid":213607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T22:24:40.000Z","msg":"割包皮預防肺炎 即刻好生意<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T22:29:45.000Z","msg":"更大可能係割包皮送肺炎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67a409ce30762ff6198c3c08c4c366c2bc04ce7d","tid":1864823,"uid":195998,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T23:35:41.000Z","msg":"人血曼頭"},{"pid":"90561d518068d357f270656ab8b7824bdb29287e","tid":1864823,"uid":1971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T23:41:38.000Z","msg":"好消極 唔洗割包皮"},{"pid":"a5f081ad3408275e83ac9a22066d2aa92cb9d9ab","tid":1864823,"uid":24570,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T23:41:48.000Z","msg":"看到路邊有美女，也趕快去廁所小便轉移注意力<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7624b077742745da7a94a8ce1924af0d780b5d50","tid":1864823,"uid":10637,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"67a409ce30762ff6198c3c08c4c366c2bc04ce7d","tid":1864823,"uid":195998,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T23:35:41.000Z","msg":"人血曼頭"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T23:42:12.000Z","msg":"個醫生又唔係靠手足賺錢<br />\n咁都人血曼頭？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf46dc3382c62e502f1db2109f67cfd6a8d5c065","tid":1864823,"uid":4574,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7624b077742745da7a94a8ce1924af0d780b5d50","tid":1864823,"uid":10637,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"67a409ce30762ff6198c3c08c4c366c2bc04ce7d","tid":1864823,"uid":195998,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T23:35:41.000Z","msg":"人血曼頭"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T23:42:12.000Z","msg":"個醫生又唔係靠手足賺錢<br />\n咁都人血曼頭？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T23:49:09.000Z","msg":"人皮饅頭"},{"pid":"15b51f59b1779f8e1a55a7a88d70ed4da368b961","tid":1864823,"uid":34828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T23:54:30.000Z","msg":"人血饅頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f26a1f857e67ecf433a6de7c1